Suhua's body?

285
00:16:42,390 --> 00:16:46,790
There is a deep cave at the foot of the mountain.

286
00:16:47,220 --> 00:16:48,720
It rained heavily a few days ago

287
00:16:48,720 --> 00:16:50,400
and several bodies were washed out.

288
00:16:50,400 --> 00:16:53,640
They were all the bodies of the girls abducted by the King of Hell.

289
00:16:53,640 --> 00:16:56,530
I recognized Suhua at first sight.

290
00:17:01,880 --> 00:17:03,120
Where are the bodies

291
00:17:03,890 --> 00:17:05,000
of the other girls?

292
00:17:05,630 --> 00:17:08,240
The families are afraid to claim the bodies

293
00:17:09,270 --> 00:17:11,090
of the girls abducted by the King of Hell.

294
00:17:11,090 --> 00:17:13,460
They are in the morgue.

295
00:17:23,130 --> 00:17:28,710
[Promote friendly relations]

296
00:17:25,040 --> 00:17:29,020
From A1 to B7 in the east of the city,

297
00:17:29,540 --> 00:17:33,099
and from C4 to D3 in the south of the city.

298
00:17:33,609 --> 00:17:34,290
Young Master,

299
00:17:34,290 --> 00:17:36,099
we've almost searched the entire Xiaoyuan City.

300
00:17:36,099 --> 00:17:39,500
But we still don't have any clues about Madam's whereabouts.

301
00:17:40,130 --> 00:17:40,930
Young Master.

302
00:17:41,990 --> 00:17:43,319
What are you looking at?

303
00:17:43,900 --> 00:17:45,359
Why is there a river pebble

304
00:17:45,660 --> 00:17:47,140
in the mine?

305
00:17:49,040 --> 00:17:49,520
Li,

306
00:17:49,849 --> 00:17:50,420
ask the government

307
00:17:50,420 --> 00:17:52,090
for Xiaoyuan City's ore record.

308
00:17:52,090 --> 00:17:53,220
Ore record?

309
00:17:53,850 --> 00:17:54,250
Okay.

310
00:17:59,720 --> 00:18:06,130
[Morgue]

311
00:18:30,670 --> 00:18:31,270
Pardon me.

312
00:18:48,660 --> 00:18:50,220
These victims indeed have

313
00:18:50,890 --> 00:18:53,340
the poison palm left over by Yunuqiao.

314
00:18:55,340 --> 00:18:58,940
Maybe it's because of this palm that the bodies haven't decayed.

315
00:18:59,460 --> 00:18:59,920
Bashi.

316
00:19:00,730 --> 00:19:03,190
Why did you say that the culprit was not the King of Hell,

317
00:19:03,190 --> 00:19:04,050
but a criminal?

318
00:19:04,100 --> 00:19:05,780
If... If he really were the King of Hell,

319
00:19:05,780 --> 00:19:07,980
why did he only appear in Xiaoyuan City?

320
00:19:08,310 --> 00:19:10,860
If the girl escapes from the city, she'll be safe.

321
00:19:10,860 --> 00:19:11,730
You're right.

322
00:19:12,310 --> 00:19:13,380
I guess this person

323
00:19:13,660 --> 00:19:15,530
used the mines to sneak out.

324
00:19:16,140 --> 00:19:17,550
Do the underground mines

325
00:19:17,970 --> 00:19:19,690
connect to the entire city?

326
00:19:19,860 --> 00:19:22,340
More than half of the houses are connected to the mines.

327
00:19:22,340 --> 00:19:26,240
But the underground mines are full of twists and turns.

328
00:19:26,410 --> 00:19:27,370
I don't know

329
00:19:27,400 --> 00:19:29,320
where they all lead to.

330
00:19:29,540 --> 00:19:31,340
It's so complicated down there,

331
00:19:31,660 --> 00:19:34,190
but he was able to find where these girls were.

332
00:19:35,190 --> 00:19:36,690
How did the King of Hell

333
00:19:36,710 --> 00:19:38,100
choose his victims,

334
00:19:39,070 --> 00:19:39,800
and how did he

335
00:19:39,820 --> 00:19:41,880
find their locations so accurately?

336
00:19:43,830 --> 00:19:44,390
Bashi.

337
00:19:45,470 --> 00:19:46,470
Did these girls

338
00:19:46,820 --> 00:19:48,220
have anything in common?

339
00:19:48,490 --> 00:19:49,650
Did they live in the same area?

340
00:19:49,650 --> 00:19:51,240
No.

341
00:19:51,400 --> 00:19:53,730
They were scattered throughout the city.

342
00:19:55,190 --> 00:19:57,050
Did they have any common friends,

343
00:19:57,110 --> 00:19:59,800
or did their families practice the same trade?

344
00:20:00,250 --> 00:20:02,780
Their families practiced different trades.

345
00:20:02,900 --> 00:20:05,220
As for common friends,

346
00:20:05,540 --> 00:20:06,900
I'm not sure.

347
00:20:06,900 --> 00:20:08,560
After all, this city is small.

348
00:20:08,730 --> 00:20:10,190
Everyone knows everyone.

349
00:20:12,660 --> 00:20:14,980
They don't seem to be related on the surface.

350
00:20:14,980 --> 00:20:16,750
But there must be a connection.

351
00:20:18,250 --> 00:20:20,980
The King of Hell has never failed in an operation.

352
00:20:21,660 --> 00:20:24,060
Even if he can travel freely under the mine,

353
00:20:24,540 --> 00:20:25,460
how did he know

354
00:20:25,460 --> 00:20:27,220
which room every girl lived in?

355
00:20:28,400 --> 00:20:30,600
He must have entered the houses before.

356
00:20:37,100 --> 00:20:37,900
Acupuncture.

357
00:20:42,450 --> 00:20:43,450
Cupping therapy.

358
00:20:51,540 --> 00:20:52,100
Bashi.

359
00:20:53,480 --> 00:20:55,970
Did Suhua see a physician before she died?

360
00:20:58,020 --> 00:21:01,290
That day, S-Suhua's mother had a headache.

361
00:21:01,560 --> 00:21:03,640
She did call a physician.

362
00:21:07,980 --> 00:21:08,500
Madam.

363
00:21:08,500 --> 00:21:10,360
The physician sent the medicine.

364
00:21:10,610 --> 00:21:11,320
That's it.

365
00:21:12,220 --> 00:21:15,050
The identity of a physician is safe and reasonable.

366
00:21:15,050 --> 00:21:17,570
He can enter a lady's house to visit her

367
00:21:18,570 --> 00:21:20,230
without arousing suspicion.

368
00:21:25,360 --> 00:21:29,140
[Xiaoyuan City]

369
00:21:31,040 --> 00:21:34,140
[Mysterious Lotus Casebook]

370
00:21:37,990 --> 00:21:38,710
[Ore Record]

371
00:21:44,180 --> 00:21:47,110
Xiaoyuan City doesn't produce white river pebbles.

372
00:21:47,380 --> 00:21:49,910
It's only found in the west, outside the city.

373
00:21:50,460 --> 00:21:51,540
Did someone

374
00:21:51,890 --> 00:21:53,550
drop it in the well on purpose?

375
00:21:55,080 --> 00:21:55,480
Li,

376
00:22:01,060 --> 00:22:02,660
have you seen any outsiders

377
00:22:02,660 --> 00:22:04,260
in and out of Baishui Garden?

378
00:22:04,700 --> 00:22:05,700
There were plenty of them.

379
00:22:05,700 --> 00:22:06,890
We hired many craftsmen

380
00:22:06,890 --> 00:22:08,550
for the renovation of the old garden.

381
00:22:08,550 --> 00:22:10,880
Was there any craftsman near the dry well?

382
00:22:12,350 --> 00:22:13,060
It's a remote place.

383
00:22:13,060 --> 00:22:14,320
Few people went there.

384
00:22:17,470 --> 00:22:18,200
What is this?

385
00:22:19,270 --> 00:22:20,740
Didn't Madam have diarrhea before?

386
00:22:20,740 --> 00:22:21,830
The physician prescribed some medicine.

387
00:22:21,830 --> 00:22:22,960
This is the residue.

388
00:22:31,280 --> 00:22:32,940
This was for diarrhea, right?

389
00:22:33,180 --> 00:22:35,320
Then why does it have xijiang grass, which is used to cure poisoning?

390
00:22:35,320 --> 00:22:37,450
It's hard for ordinary people to tell.

391
00:22:37,720 --> 00:22:39,220
If it weren't for people like us

392
00:22:39,220 --> 00:22:41,140
who have been miners for decades,

393
00:22:41,350 --> 00:22:42,950
who can tell the difference?

394
00:22:43,630 --> 00:22:45,020
Where was the physician mixing the herbs?

395
00:22:45,020 --> 00:22:46,880
In the side hall near the dry well.

396
00:22:48,780 --> 00:22:49,460
It's him.

397
00:22:49,880 --> 00:22:50,810
What do you mean?

398
00:22:51,060 --> 00:22:53,300
Not many people know about the emerald jade's poison.

399
00:22:53,300 --> 00:22:55,700
But he prescribed the antidote right away.

400
00:22:55,860 --> 00:22:56,780
It seems that he must know about

401
00:22:56,780 --> 00:22:58,240
the situation of the mine.

402
00:22:58,620 --> 00:22:59,750
He marked this place

403
00:23:00,270 --> 00:23:01,220
by tossing the white river pebble into the well

404
00:23:01,220 --> 00:23:02,820
when he was mixing the herbs.

405
00:23:02,880 --> 00:23:03,370
Li,

406
00:23:03,700 --> 00:23:05,030
light the signal smoke.

407
00:23:45,120 --> 00:23:46,800
[Physician Xue]

408
00:23:47,350 --> 00:23:48,310
It's you.

409
00:23:49,490 --> 00:23:51,150
The physician who treated me.

410
00:23:51,300 --> 00:23:52,100
It's too late.

411
00:24:10,450 --> 00:24:11,510
What are you doing?

412
00:24:11,710 --> 00:24:12,390
Listen.

413
00:24:12,890 --> 00:24:14,490
If you dare lay a finger on me,

414
00:24:14,640 --> 00:24:16,300
my son will never forgive you.

415
00:24:26,900 --> 00:24:27,570
Li Lianhua!

416
00:24:29,140 --> 00:24:31,330
Looks like I arrived just in time.

417
00:24:31,460 --> 00:24:32,050
Be careful.

418
00:24:32,050 --> 00:24:33,570
There's poison on his palms.

419
00:24:33,570 --> 00:24:35,510
The murderer pretends to be a physician.

420
00:24:35,510 --> 00:24:36,910
You sure know how to hide.

421
00:24:51,130 --> 00:24:52,060
Why are you here?

422
00:24:52,740 --> 00:24:54,200
Let's talk about it later.

423
00:24:54,390 --> 00:24:55,190
Fang Xiaobao.

424
00:24:55,260 --> 00:24:56,090
What took you so long?

425
00:24:56,090 --> 00:24:56,570
Mother!

426
00:24:56,850 --> 00:24:58,170
Catch that bastard!

427
00:24:59,110 --> 00:25:01,460
Few people know about the emerald jade's poison.

428
00:25:01,460 --> 00:25:03,870
But you prescribed the antidote right away.

429
00:25:03,870 --> 00:25:05,200
This white river pebble

430
00:25:05,490 --> 00:25:08,220
was also a mark you threw into the dry well, right?

431
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:14,650
The Bizhong Strike might be powerful,

432
00:25:14,650 --> 00:25:16,460
but the toxin in his body is limited.

433
00:25:16,460 --> 00:25:17,080
I'll attack the shaoyang channel,

434
00:25:17,080 --> 00:25:17,910
and you attack the queyin channel.

435
00:25:17,910 --> 00:25:19,390
This way, he can't channel the poison.

436
00:25:19,390 --> 00:25:20,660
How dare you abduct my mother?

437
00:25:20,660 --> 00:25:22,060
You're asking for death.

438
00:25:36,690 --> 00:25:37,890
Be careful, Xiaobao.

439
00:25:53,650 --> 00:25:54,310
Don't move.

440
00:26:04,590 --> 00:26:05,510
You're here too.

441
00:26:05,510 --> 00:26:06,840
After receiving your news,

442
00:26:06,840 --> 00:26:08,270
we set up a trap here

443
00:26:08,340 --> 00:26:09,200
and caught him.

444
00:26:09,220 --> 00:26:10,480
Did you see Li Lianhua?

445
00:26:11,100 --> 00:26:13,260
Didn't the two of you lock him in the post?

446
00:26:13,260 --> 00:26:14,140
He is cunning.

447
00:26:14,420 --> 00:26:15,870
He picked the lock and escaped.

448
00:26:15,870 --> 00:26:16,990
Look out for him.

449
00:26:17,270 --> 00:26:18,390
I'll bring him to justice.

450
00:26:18,390 --> 00:26:20,190
We're taking this suspect away for interrogation.

451
00:26:20,190 --> 00:26:22,190
Come to the post to find us later.

452
00:26:22,430 --> 00:26:22,760
Okay.

453
00:26:25,940 --> 00:26:26,600
Xiaobao.

454
00:26:27,910 --> 00:26:29,240
Where did Li Lianhua go?

455
00:26:30,420 --> 00:26:31,750
This guy is up to no good.

456
00:26:31,830 --> 00:26:33,630
He'd be caught if he stayed here.

457
00:26:34,530 --> 00:26:36,860
Your mother almost got poisoned just now.

458
00:26:37,210 --> 00:26:38,570
Li Lianhua saved me.

459
00:26:39,030 --> 00:26:39,900
How could you say that

460
00:26:39,900 --> 00:26:41,550
my savior is up to no good?

461
00:26:42,060 --> 00:26:42,940
How heartless.

462
00:26:44,120 --> 00:26:45,180
By the way, Mother.

463
00:26:45,740 --> 00:26:46,430
Are you okay?

464
00:26:46,430 --> 00:26:47,220
Are you hurt?

465
00:26:48,410 --> 00:26:49,620
Of course not.

466
00:26:51,220 --> 00:26:52,570
That darn physician

467
00:26:52,600 --> 00:26:54,130
caught me off guard, is all.

468
00:26:54,700 --> 00:26:56,360
But he's no better.

469
00:26:56,740 --> 00:26:59,440
He was struck by my Bone-breaking Pearl.

470
00:26:59,860 --> 00:27:01,590
He'll be suffering for a while.

471
00:27:01,600 --> 00:27:03,150
I'm glad you didn't get hurt.

472
00:27:03,150 --> 00:27:04,610
I was so worried about you.

473
00:27:04,680 --> 00:27:05,210
Alright.

474
00:27:05,460 --> 00:27:06,520
I'll take you home.

475
00:27:06,770 --> 00:27:08,300
Invite Li Lianhua over next time.

476
00:27:08,300 --> 00:27:09,660
I need to thank him properly.

477
00:27:09,660 --> 00:27:10,140
Alright.

478
00:27:10,140 --> 00:27:10,980
Got it.

479
00:27:14,960 --> 00:27:15,600
Water.

480
00:27:16,720 --> 00:27:18,560
Water. Give me water.

481
00:27:19,750 --> 00:27:20,220
Water.

482
00:27:21,310 --> 00:27:22,120
Give me water.

483
00:27:22,470 --> 00:27:24,590
Water! Water!

484
00:27:25,400 --> 00:27:26,920
There are too many toxins in his body.

485
00:27:26,920 --> 00:27:28,580
He didn't get to detoxify using Yunuqiao.

486
00:27:28,580 --> 00:27:30,730
So he desperately needs water to dilute the poison.

487
00:27:30,730 --> 00:27:31,330
Take it.

488
00:27:31,750 --> 00:27:33,750
The thing you want is in my boot.

489
00:27:35,270 --> 00:27:36,360
Give me water!

490
00:27:42,820 --> 00:27:44,300
Water! Water!

491
00:27:46,120 --> 00:27:47,700
Water.

492
00:27:48,460 --> 00:27:49,030
Water.

493
00:27:50,220 --> 00:27:51,980
Give me water.

494
00:27:53,170 --> 00:27:54,140
Water!

495
00:27:54,880 --> 00:27:56,960
Water!

496
00:28:06,380 --> 00:28:06,980
Lian Quan.

497
00:28:07,780 --> 00:28:09,710
This must be the Rama Heavenly Ice.

498
00:28:11,170 --> 00:28:13,490
I can't believe that, apart from the Jinyuan Alliance,

499
00:28:13,490 --> 00:28:16,750
even Baichuan Court knows about the Rama Heavenly Ice now.

500
00:28:17,030 --> 00:28:17,910
Not only that,

501
00:28:18,260 --> 00:28:20,150
but we also know about the searing karmic fire.

502
00:28:20,150 --> 00:28:20,980
So you'd better tell us

503
00:28:20,980 --> 00:28:23,310
about the Nanyin people's plan back then.

504
00:28:23,400 --> 00:28:25,570
Otherwise, in a few hours,

505
00:28:25,970 --> 00:28:28,630
you won't get another pail of water to detoxify with.

506
00:28:28,630 --> 00:28:29,430
I'll tell you.

507
00:28:30,350 --> 00:28:31,540
Look at me now.

508
00:28:32,170 --> 00:28:34,030
There's nothing I can't tell you.

509
00:28:34,500 --> 00:28:36,920
Back then, my ancestors and the other three individuals

510
00:28:36,920 --> 00:28:39,360
came to the Central Plains with the Rama Heavenly Ices.

511
00:28:39,360 --> 00:28:41,620
We planned to open the Rama Vessel one day

512
00:28:41,870 --> 00:28:44,600
and use it to control the millions of Midlanders.

513
00:28:45,860 --> 00:28:47,830
But the four guarding the Rama Heavenly Ices

514
00:28:47,830 --> 00:28:49,490
eventually led a wealthy life

515
00:28:49,830 --> 00:28:51,310
and didn't want to partake

516
00:28:51,690 --> 00:28:53,750
in such a dangerous venture anymore.

517
00:28:53,830 --> 00:28:55,900
I didn't expect that after all these years,

518
00:28:55,900 --> 00:28:57,700
I escaped the Jinyuan Alliance,

519
00:28:58,200 --> 00:28:59,960
but couldn't escape Baichuan Court.

520
00:28:59,960 --> 00:29:00,820
Many years ago,

521
00:29:01,200 --> 00:29:02,670
I met the Lord of the Netherworld

522
00:29:02,670 --> 00:29:03,880
once.

523
00:29:05,300 --> 00:29:07,870
Why do you look so different from him?

524
00:29:11,430 --> 00:29:13,530
I accidentally used the emerald jade to practice

525
00:29:13,530 --> 00:29:14,770
and was badly poisoned.

526
00:29:14,770 --> 00:29:16,410
My appearance had long changed.

527
00:29:16,410 --> 00:29:18,750
If I hadn't used the Sanskrit technique to change my skin,

528
00:29:18,750 --> 00:29:20,410
I wouldn't even appear human.

529
00:29:20,410 --> 00:29:22,070
A Sanskrit technique for changing your skin?

530
00:29:22,070 --> 00:29:23,470
It's a secret technique.

531
00:29:23,710 --> 00:29:25,310
Only a few enlightened monks

532
00:29:25,490 --> 00:29:28,090
can acquire the method from the Sanskrit scripts.

533
00:29:28,090 --> 00:29:29,390
It can transform a person anew

534
00:29:29,390 --> 00:29:31,190
and completely change one's appearance.

535
00:29:31,190 --> 00:29:33,320
Completely change one's appearance?

536
00:29:34,930 --> 00:29:37,780
All right, I've told you everything I know.

537
00:29:38,240 --> 00:29:40,170
You also got the Rama Heavenly Ice.

538
00:29:40,440 --> 00:29:41,370
Please let me go.

539
00:29:41,480 --> 00:29:42,410
Let you go?

540
00:29:42,850 --> 00:29:43,860
Have you ever let those girls

541
00:29:43,860 --> 00:29:45,390
who were murdered by you go?

542
00:29:46,470 --> 00:29:48,110
I'll make you pay

543
00:29:48,820 --> 00:29:51,350
for all your crimes.

544
00:29:53,060 --> 00:29:54,660
This is an important matter.

545
00:29:54,770 --> 00:29:56,620
I'm going to ask the All-Knowing Mr. Su

546
00:29:56,620 --> 00:29:58,820
to verify whether the Ice is real or not.

547
00:29:59,340 --> 00:30:01,270
I'll leave you to escort Lian Quan.

548
00:30:01,770 --> 00:30:02,630
Let’s split up.

549
00:30:04,570 --> 00:30:06,230
Since the Rama Heavenly Ice is so important,

550
00:30:06,230 --> 00:30:08,430
I can’t let you go off on your own with it.

551
00:30:08,560 --> 00:30:09,760
I should go with you.

552
00:30:11,520 --> 00:30:12,920
You still don't trust me,

553
00:30:13,840 --> 00:30:14,260
right?

554
00:30:16,040 --> 00:30:18,170
It's only right that I don't trust you.

555
00:30:18,390 --> 00:30:19,470
If we go together,

556
00:30:20,150 --> 00:30:21,650
what will happen to Lian Quan?

557
00:30:21,650 --> 00:30:23,380
Should we leave him at the post?

558
00:30:23,740 --> 00:30:24,940
Fang Duobing is here.

559
00:30:25,750 --> 00:30:26,720
It's safer to lock Lian Quan

560
00:30:26,720 --> 00:30:28,420
in the Baishui Garden bought by the Fang family

561
00:30:28,420 --> 00:30:29,790
than in the post.

562
00:30:30,920 --> 00:30:32,000
You need not worry.

563
00:30:35,020 --> 00:30:35,460
Okay.

564
00:30:36,290 --> 00:30:37,290
Come with me then.

