I think he is.

574
00:30:58,250 --> 00:31:01,180
I'll find a way to make him talk in the next three days.

575
00:31:12,470 --> 00:31:13,070
Bashi.

576
00:31:13,880 --> 00:31:14,940
You're so skilled.

577
00:31:15,430 --> 00:31:18,580
