592
00:31:46,970 --> 00:31:48,190
Two fried dough sticks.

593
00:31:48,190 --> 00:31:48,710
Okay.

594
00:31:48,850 --> 00:31:50,180
I'll put the money here.

595
00:31:54,260 --> 00:31:54,730
Bashi.

596
00:31:55,550 --> 00:31:56,870
Why did you put the money

597
00:31:56,870 --> 00:31:58,040
in a bowl of water?

598
00:31:58,170 --> 00:32:01,060
M-my hands are greasy.

599
00:32:01,080 --> 00:32:03,410
I dirty the money when I touch them.

600
00:32:05,270 --> 00:32:05,710
I see.

601
00:32:24,580 --> 00:32:25,440
Incense ashes.

602
00:32:41,830 --> 00:32:44,090
Tianji Hall's products are all the best.

603
00:32:44,620 --> 00:32:46,220
This Liushui octagonal cage

604
00:32:46,380 --> 00:32:48,580
was specially built overnight for you.

605
00:33:07,930 --> 00:33:10,710
The flowing water will help you detoxify and keep you alive.

606
00:33:10,710 --> 00:33:12,250
Very considerate, isn't it?

607
00:33:12,250 --> 00:33:12,890
But...

608
00:33:19,570 --> 00:33:21,970
If you don't tell us who your accomplice is,

609
00:33:22,020 --> 00:33:24,750
you won't be able to enjoy the life-saving water.

610
00:33:26,110 --> 00:33:27,110
What accomplice?

611
00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:28,440
Stop pretending.

612
00:33:29,020 --> 00:33:30,170
When I chased you that day,

613
00:33:30,170 --> 00:33:31,570
someone covered for you.

614
00:33:31,840 --> 00:33:33,500
Did the poison enter your brain

615
00:33:33,500 --> 00:33:34,630
