616
00:33:34,980 --> 00:33:36,580
That was just a thief I hired.

617
00:33:37,450 --> 00:33:38,880
Every time I abduct someone,

618
00:33:38,880 --> 00:33:41,610
I hire a thief from the underworld to act as a decoy

619
00:33:41,810 --> 00:33:43,070
so I can strike easily.

620
00:33:43,810 --> 00:33:46,330
I pay them when the deed is done

621
00:33:46,750 --> 00:33:47,840
and we never associate with each other again.

622
00:33:47,840 --> 00:33:49,450
Never associate with each other again?

623
00:33:49,450 --> 00:33:50,580
That can't be right.

624
00:33:50,880 --> 00:33:53,340
I remember my mother's Bone-breaking Pearl

625
00:33:53,380 --> 00:33:55,460
landed a solid hit on the intruder.

626
00:33:56,320 --> 00:33:58,300
The Bone-breaking Pearl strikes deep into the bones.

627
00:33:58,300 --> 00:33:59,210
But just now,

628
00:34:00,400 --> 00:34:02,330
I saw no trace of such injury on you.

629
00:34:02,810 --> 00:34:03,920
The only explanation is,

630
00:34:03,920 --> 00:34:06,220
you were not the one struck by the Bone-breaking Pearl.

631
00:34:06,220 --> 00:34:06,980
It's possible that you hired a thief

632
00:34:06,980 --> 00:34:08,610
to abduct someone for you.

633
00:34:09,190 --> 00:34:11,400
But to bear the Bone-breaking Pearl for you,

634
00:34:11,400 --> 00:34:12,930
that's not worth the price.

635
00:34:13,700 --> 00:34:14,160
Tell me.

636
00:34:14,910 --> 00:34:16,370
Where is your accomplice?

637
00:34:19,930 --> 00:34:21,260
You're quite stubborn.

638
00:34:22,460 --> 00:34:23,320
Ms. He, please.

639
00:34:29,000 --> 00:34:30,890
It's been a long time since I made a mechanism overnight.

640
00:34:30,890 --> 00:34:31,820
Because of you,

641
00:34:31,850 --> 00:34:33,090
I stayed up all night.

642
00:34:35,739 --> 00:34:37,070
These mechanical hands

643
00:34:37,230 --> 00:34:40,190
specialize in poking the most itchy and painful acupoints.

644
00:34:40,190 --> 00:34:42,420
