645
00:34:42,420 --> 00:34:44,310
Sometimes, it'll make you cry out of pain.

646
00:34:44,310 --> 00:34:47,120
Other times, it'll make you laugh till you're breathless.

647
00:34:47,120 --> 00:34:47,920
Be sensible.

648
00:34:48,080 --> 00:34:49,290
Just answer

649
00:34:49,310 --> 00:34:50,770
whatever Xiaobao asks.

650
00:34:51,060 --> 00:34:52,870
Otherwise, prepare to suffer.

651
00:35:06,739 --> 00:35:07,219
Tell me.

652
00:35:07,699 --> 00:35:09,100
Where is the accomplice?

653
00:35:12,239 --> 00:35:14,389
Looks like you're prepared to die.

654
00:35:14,710 --> 00:35:15,590
Let me tell you.

655
00:35:15,810 --> 00:35:18,639
I haven't settled the scores with you for abducting me.

656
00:35:18,639 --> 00:35:20,570
Let's see how long you can hold out.

657
00:35:23,610 --> 00:35:24,210
By the way,

658
00:35:24,620 --> 00:35:26,550
I haven't named the mechanism yet.

659
00:35:27,660 --> 00:35:31,260
Let's call it the Lotus Acupoint Fingers.

660
00:35:32,020 --> 00:35:32,820
Fang Xiaobao.

661
00:35:32,890 --> 00:35:33,900
What do you think?

662
00:35:34,510 --> 00:35:35,970
Call me when he confesses.

663
00:35:38,300 --> 00:35:39,070
You brat.

664
00:35:39,510 --> 00:35:41,170
You're good at avoiding work.

665
00:35:47,060 --> 00:35:49,490
[Hanshui Temple]

666
00:35:58,910 --> 00:36:00,510
Master, you're so composed.

667
00:36:00,660 --> 00:36:03,190
The Bone-breaking Pearl must have hurt a lot.

668
00:36:03,820 --> 00:36:04,530
Oh, wait.

669
00:36:06,310 --> 00:36:07,910
I shouldn't call you Master.

670
00:36:08,350 --> 00:36:10,790
Should I call you Niutou,

671
00:36:11,610 --> 00:36:12,530
or Mamian?

672
00:36:13,850 --> 00:36:15,170
Didn't you see

673
00:36:15,510 --> 00:36:17,690
Niutou Manian's bodies in the mine?

674
00:36:19,120 --> 00:36:19,920
You're right.

675
00:36:20,400 --> 00:36:20,990
Yes.

676
00:36:21,380 --> 00:36:22,690
When I first saw

677
00:36:23,170 --> 00:36:24,630
the two bodies in the mine,

678
00:36:25,020 --> 00:36:27,420
I did suspect that they were Niutou Mamian.

679
00:36:28,210 --> 00:36:29,670
But out of the two corpses,

680
00:36:30,300 --> 00:36:33,310
one was heavier than the other.

681
00:36:34,020 --> 00:36:35,420
The legless body had

682
00:36:35,550 --> 00:36:37,160
a much wider pelvis bone.

683
00:36:37,480 --> 00:36:38,740
It belonged to a woman.

684
00:36:38,810 --> 00:36:41,110
So the people who died in the mine

685
00:36:41,140 --> 00:36:42,620
were not Niutou Mamian,

686
00:36:43,180 --> 00:36:44,940
but Lian Quan and his wife.

687
00:36:45,200 --> 00:36:46,200
Am I right?

688
00:36:47,020 --> 00:36:49,350
Smart people are indeed hard to deal with.

689
00:36:49,730 --> 00:36:52,170
But you're only half right.

690
00:36:53,500 --> 00:36:55,360
You killed Lian Quan and his wife,

691
00:36:55,670 --> 00:36:57,060
stole Lian Quan's secret book,

692
00:36:57,060 --> 00:37:00,310
and mastered the Bizhong Strike. But you feared being hunted by his enemies,

693
00:37:00,310 --> 00:37:01,940
so you disguised Lian Quan and his wife's bodies

694
00:37:01,940 --> 00:37:03,780
into their current state.

695
00:37:04,340 --> 00:37:04,910
Right?

696
00:37:05,510 --> 00:37:08,240
We didn't kill Lian Quan for his martial arts.

697
00:37:09,100 --> 00:37:10,830
We did it to protect ourselves.

698
00:37:26,410 --> 00:37:27,330
Many years ago,

699
00:37:27,670 --> 00:37:30,970
we were discriminated against by others for our appearance.

700
00:37:30,970 --> 00:37:32,960
But Lian Quan thought highly of us.

701
00:37:33,280 --> 00:37:34,690
We were very grateful.

702
00:37:35,010 --> 00:37:38,130
So, when the Jinyuan Alliance surrounded Lian Quan's mansion

703
00:37:38,130 --> 00:37:39,810
for the Rama Heavenly Ice,

704
00:37:40,160 --> 00:37:42,160
we risked our lives to help him escape

705
00:37:41,490 --> 00:37:43,350
[Niutou, Li Xiao]

706
00:37:41,490 --> 00:37:43,350
[Mamian, Li Xiong]

707
00:37:42,670 --> 00:37:45,070
and fled to Xiaoyuan City to live in hiding.

708
00:37:45,710 --> 00:37:46,970
But he married

709
00:37:46,990 --> 00:37:49,000
a frivolous woman here,

710
00:37:49,170 --> 00:37:50,690
and started to suspect us.

711
00:37:51,420 --> 00:37:54,030
He thought we were preying on that woman.

712
00:37:55,040 --> 00:37:57,040
Lian Quan lured us into the mine

713
00:37:57,350 --> 00:37:59,050
with the excuse of teaching us Bizhong Strike.

714
00:37:59,050 --> 00:38:00,580
Then, he made us practice on

715
00:38:00,660 --> 00:38:02,890
the poisonous emerald jade instead of emerald.

716
00:38:02,890 --> 00:38:05,690
By the time we found out, we were already poisoned.

717
00:38:06,840 --> 00:38:09,640
He thought we would die down there from the poison.

718
00:38:09,750 --> 00:38:12,610
But my younger brother, Li Xiong, reversed the skill

719
00:38:12,610 --> 00:38:15,010
and transferred all the toxins to himself.

720
00:38:15,160 --> 00:38:16,890
Then, he separated our bodies.

721
00:38:17,390 --> 00:38:18,940
Although I lost my lower limbs,

722
00:38:18,940 --> 00:38:20,000
I was not poisoned.

723
00:38:20,680 --> 00:38:22,490
I was able to move with the help of mechanisms.

724
00:38:22,490 --> 00:38:25,570
But my brother was poisoned and in critical condition.

725
00:38:25,620 --> 00:38:26,150
Brother.

726
00:38:26,870 --> 00:38:27,400
Brother!

727
00:38:27,510 --> 00:38:28,150
Don't!

728
00:38:28,290 --> 00:38:28,820
Brother!

729
00:38:30,260 --> 00:38:32,210
I was in a hurry to save my brother's life

730
00:38:32,210 --> 00:38:33,500
and tried many ways.

731
00:38:33,980 --> 00:38:36,300
Then, I finally found out that the abbot of Hanshui Temple

732
00:38:36,300 --> 00:38:39,260
owned the Yunuqiao mental codes that could detoxicate and save lives.

733
00:38:36,360 --> 00:38:41,320
[Hanshui Temple]

734
00:38:39,830 --> 00:38:43,230
I killed the abbot, stole the book, and kept my brother alive.

735
00:38:43,420 --> 00:38:44,100
After that,

736
00:38:44,270 --> 00:38:46,250
I used the identity of the abbot of Hanshui Temple

737
00:38:45,300 --> 00:38:46,960
[Hanshui Temple]

738
00:38:46,490 --> 00:38:47,950
to remain in Xiaoyuan City

739
00:38:47,960 --> 00:38:49,740
-and take revenge on Lian Quan.
-Brother.

740
00:38:49,740 --> 00:38:50,070
Look.

741
00:38:50,820 --> 00:38:51,430
I found it.

742
00:38:52,920 --> 00:38:54,960
[Yunuqiao Mental Codes]

743
00:38:57,240 --> 00:38:57,760
Madam.

744
00:38:58,090 --> 00:38:59,020
At last, one day,

745
00:38:59,910 --> 00:39:02,110
I managed to lure Lian Quan into the mine

746
00:39:02,590 --> 00:39:04,250
and killed him and that woman.

747
00:39:04,700 --> 00:39:05,570
Then, I disguised the bodies

748
00:39:05,570 --> 00:39:07,130
to look like us.

749
00:39:08,000 --> 00:39:10,790
This way, even if the Jinyuan Alliance finds out,

750
00:39:11,860 --> 00:39:13,630
they won't suspect us.

751
00:39:20,580 --> 00:39:22,460
Everything was perfect.

752
00:39:22,980 --> 00:39:24,970
But while we avoided the Jinyuan Alliance,

753
00:39:24,970 --> 00:39:26,500
we couldn't avoid you guys.

754
00:39:26,680 --> 00:39:27,790
My brother, Lee Xiong,

755
00:39:27,790 --> 00:39:29,250
has been captured, right?

756
00:39:30,060 --> 00:39:31,630
He's in the hands of the Baichuan Court.

757
00:39:31,630 --> 00:39:33,830
Fortunately, I'm not that unlucky.

758
00:39:34,500 --> 00:39:36,320
God gave me

759
00:39:36,340 --> 00:39:37,580
a chance to survive.

760
00:39:37,960 --> 00:39:39,760
Your identity has been exposed.

761
00:39:39,970 --> 00:39:41,430
You still want to survive?

762
00:39:41,620 --> 00:39:43,890
With Li Xiangyi, the leader of the Sigu Sect here,

763
00:39:43,890 --> 00:39:44,920
of course I can.

764
00:39:45,740 --> 00:39:48,520
That day, you used Whirling Steps when you were chasing me.

765
00:39:48,520 --> 00:39:49,380
Sect Leader Li,

766
00:39:49,650 --> 00:39:50,820
you can't fool me.

767
00:39:51,190 --> 00:39:52,520
If it were Lee Xiangyi,

768
00:39:54,110 --> 00:39:56,110
