781
00:40:24,060 --> 00:40:26,070
But now I have you, Li Xiangyi.

782
00:40:26,380 --> 00:40:27,770
I can give the Ice away.

783
00:40:28,340 --> 00:40:29,200
Sect Leader Li.

784
00:40:29,410 --> 00:40:30,070
Promise me,

785
00:40:30,260 --> 00:40:31,880
and the Rama Heavenly Ice is yours.

786
00:40:31,880 --> 00:40:34,260
Otherwise, I'll hand it over to the Jinyuan Alliance.

787
00:40:34,260 --> 00:40:36,180
Although they are not as trustworthy as you,

788
00:40:36,180 --> 00:40:38,580
they're still capable of keeping us alive.

789
00:40:39,420 --> 00:40:40,020
Tell me.

790
00:40:40,780 --> 00:40:42,110
What do you want me to do?

791
00:40:43,630 --> 00:40:44,960
Save my brother Li Xiong

792
00:40:45,210 --> 00:40:47,210
and cure his Bizhong Strike poison.

793
00:40:47,510 --> 00:40:48,120
I know.

794
00:40:48,830 --> 00:40:51,760
The Yangzhouman is the best inner power in the world.

795
00:40:51,930 --> 00:40:53,660
