796
00:40:54,250 --> 00:40:54,940
Li Xiao.

797
00:40:55,500 --> 00:40:56,830
You're too optimistic.

798
00:40:57,460 --> 00:40:59,810
I'm no longer a member of the Baichuan Court.

799
00:40:59,810 --> 00:41:02,290
