800
00:41:02,550 --> 00:41:04,430
I can't save your brother.

801
00:41:04,900 --> 00:41:06,540
That's your problem now.

802
00:41:06,820 --> 00:41:08,350
It has nothing to do with me.

803
00:41:08,460 --> 00:41:11,390
I know you're close to Fang Duobing,

804
00:41:11,420 --> 00:41:13,280
the detective of Baichuan Court.

805
00:41:13,720 --> 00:41:15,720
