806
00:41:16,370 --> 00:41:16,890
Finally,

807
00:41:16,890 --> 00:41:18,670
Sect Leader Li, let me remind you.

808
00:41:18,670 --> 00:41:19,930
You only have two days.

809
00:41:19,990 --> 00:41:20,860
Once the time is up,

810
00:41:20,860 --> 00:41:23,060
I'll ask the Jinyuan Alliance for help.

811
00:41:23,600 --> 00:41:24,730
You better hurry up.

812
00:41:26,230 --> 00:41:28,620
Looks like I'll have to offend Fang Xiaobao again.

813
00:41:28,620 --> 00:41:30,480
It's not a big deal to promise you.

814
00:41:30,530 --> 00:41:32,750
But I'm worried.

815
00:41:34,310 --> 00:41:35,170
Sect Leader Li.

816
00:41:35,820 --> 00:41:37,160
What are you worried about?

817
00:41:37,160 --> 00:41:38,710
Your brother's Ice is fake.

818
00:41:39,220 --> 00:41:41,700
I have to check if your Ice

819
00:41:41,850 --> 00:41:42,850
is real.

820
00:41:50,290 --> 00:41:51,950
Li Xiangyi is a man of his word.

821
00:41:52,300 --> 00:41:54,560
I believe you won’t take the treasure by force.

822
00:41:54,560 --> 00:41:57,160
