823
00:41:57,160 --> 00:41:58,420
I'm only confirming its authenticity.

824
00:41:58,420 --> 00:41:59,880
I won't snatch it from you.

825
00:42:17,310 --> 00:42:17,850
Deal.

826
00:42:20,360 --> 00:42:21,160
Fang Xiaobao.

827
00:42:21,740 --> 00:42:23,270
Why did you lock the prison?

828
00:42:23,830 --> 00:42:25,890
The physician hasn't confessed yet.

829
00:42:27,100 --> 00:42:27,740
Your mechanism poked him

830
00:42:27,740 --> 00:42:29,790
